From inside a `NavigationStack`, you can use the `.toolbar` modifier to add a `.cancellationAction` toolbar item which will take the place of the built in cancel button. i.e.
```NavigationStack {
    MyContent()
    .sheet(isPresented: $isPresented) {
        MyModalContent()
        .toolbar {
            ToolbarItem(placement: .cancellationAction) {
                Button("Cancel") {
                    // dismiss sheet here    
                }
            }
        }
    }
}```

